# Study Project Planning Focus

## Rules
- Prioritize production-grade outcomes and practical learning.
- Emphasize three areas: AI infrastructure fundamentals, agent engineering, and cost optimization.
- For each proposed step, state the learning objective.
- Prefer realistic production-ready options with clear reliability and maintainability expectations.
- Include expected cost impact and key trade-offs.
- When multiple options exist, choose the best value/learning/complexity balance.

## Planning Output
- Current objective
- Learning goal
- Next step
- AI infrastructure focus
- Agent focus
- Production-grade note
- Cost note
